{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-05_311","head":{"value":"[Ballade]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1702 [tome 6], p. 311-314.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"La piece qui suit sur l’immaculée Conception de la Vierge, a remporté le prix de la Ballade, au Palinod de Caën. Elle a esté faite sur ce que les Dieux voulans punir la temerité de Promethée qui avoit derobé le feu du Ciel, il fut attaché à un Rocher sur le Mont Caucase, où un Vautour venoit tous les jours luy ronger le cœur sans pouvoir le faire mourir, &amp; le sang qui couloit de ce cœur, arrosant la terre en faisoit sortir une fleur qui ne se pouvoit ternir.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"lg":{"label":{"value":"BALLADE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/label"},"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour avoir pris le feu des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ton supplice est insuportable :","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de tes cris, ô miserable,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En vain tu fatigues les Dieux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais s’ils n’écoutent pas tes vœux,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils font dans ce tourment terrible,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Naistre de ton sang glorieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’unique fleur incorruptible.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si-tost que ce Vautour affreux,","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui déchire ton cœur coupable,","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En tire un sang inépuisable ;","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour punir ton crime odieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sort-il pas devant tes yeux,","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O prodige incomprehensible !","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du lieu le plus infructueux","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’unique fleur incoruptible.","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il fasse un vent impetueux,","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il tombe une gresle effroyable,","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où que du Ciel même implacable ;","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La foudre tombe dans ces lieux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toûjours ce germe prétieux","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans éprouver rien de nuisible","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sera malgré ces temps fâcheux","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’unique fleur incoruptible.","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"label":{"value":"ALLUSION.","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/label"},"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce Criminel audacieux","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont le sort fut si déplorable","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous montre aujourd’huy son semblable","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le premier de nos ayeux :","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais ton portrait miraculeux","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vierge, en cette plainte est visible,","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu sors d’entre les vicieux","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’unique fleur incoruptible.","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}